People always say, every secret shared, should stay within the circle of trust.
Always remember, secrets are valuable.
So, safeguard them like precious jewels.
Seldom should one divulge information that is confidential.
Wise is the person who knows the value of silence.
Others may not always have your best interests at heart.
Remember, discretion is the better part of valor.
Diligence in keeping secrets is a virtue.


*IMPORTANT NOTE*: Do note that the password is case-sensitive! (This sentence is not part of the password)
